    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the Late Assyrian period from 721 to 627 BCE, during the rule of the dynasty founded by Sargon II and including his successors, Sennacherib, Esarhaddon, and Assurbanipal.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere al período Asirio Tardío de 721 al 627 a.C., durante el reinado de la dinastía fundada por Sargon II incluyendo a sus sucesores, Sennacherib, Esarhaddon, y Assurbanipal.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar de laat-Assyrische periode van 721 tot 627 v. Chr., tijdens de heerschappij van de door Sargon II gestichte dynastie en zijn opvolgers, Sennacherib, Esarhaddon, en Assurbanipal.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指自西元前721年至西元前627年間，在王朝開創者薩爾貢二世（Sargon II）及其繼承者西拿基立（Sennacherib）、以撒哈頓（Esarhaddon）與亞述巴尼帕（Assurbanipal）統治下所發展的晚亞述時代。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
